1992年10月，[[三星电影公司|三星电影公司]]和[[史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格|史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格]]的{{link-en|安伯林娱乐公司|Amblin Entertainment}}计划在第二年开始拍摄一部佐罗题材的电影，并请来乔尔·格罗斯撰写剧本，他之前改编[[大仲马|大仲马]]名著《[[三剑客|三剑客]]》的剧本给公司留下了深刻的印象<ref>{{cite news|first=John Evan|last=Frook|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR101139|title=TriStar Pix kicks off 'Rudy' film|date=1992-10-14|work=Variety|accessdate=2010-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106180858/http://www.variety.com/article/VR101139|archive-date=2012-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=John Evan|last=Frook|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR101521|title='Musketeers' vs. Mouseketeers|date=1992-11-23|work=Variety|accessdate=2010-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106180921/http://www.variety.com/article/VR101521|archive-date=2012-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，一开始斯皮尔伯格还有可能会亲自执导这部影片<ref>{{cite news | first = Claudia | last = Eller | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR103598 | title = Nicholson, Nolte, Mancuso team | date = 1993-02-01 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2010-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106180943/http://www.variety.com/article/VR103598 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。格罗斯于1993年3月完成了剧本，三星也在同一个月就开始了影片的前期准备工作，并在当月的{{link-en|国家影院业主协会|National Association of Theatre Owners}}举行的一场名为“ShoWest”展会上为影片作了推广<ref>{{cite news | first = John Evan | last = Frook | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR103707 | title = TriStar slate reflects '93 about-'Face' | date = 1993-02-04 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2010-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106181010/http://www.variety.com/article/VR103707 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = John Evan | last = Frook | title = TriStar slate stellar at NATO | work = Variety | date = 1993-03-10 | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR104840 | accessdate = 2011-01-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121107083126/http://www.variety.com/article/VR104840 | archive-date = 2012-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1993年12月，{{link-en|布朗科·路斯蒂格|Branko Lustig}}与斯皮尔伯格一起参与影片制片工作，而迈克尔·塞洛蒙将出任导演<ref>{{cite news | first = John Evan | last = Frook | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR116401 | title = TriStar develops full dance card for '94-95 | date = 1993-12-09 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2010-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106181045/http://www.variety.com/article/VR116401 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1994年8月，[[肖恩·康纳利|肖恩·康纳利]]被选中出演唐·迪亚哥·德拉维加一角，而塞洛蒙则确保其他几个主要角色都将由西班牙裔或拉丁裔演员出演。前制工作一直进行到了8月，塞洛蒙拍摄了样片并计划于1995年4月正式开拍<ref>{{cite news | first = Army | last = Archerd | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117862531 | title = Sean Connery, As Diego De La Vega | date = 1994-08-04 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2010-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106181110/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117862531 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

康纳利和塞洛蒙之后都退出了电影的拍摄，直至1995年9月，因《{{link-en|杀人三步曲|Desperado (film)}}》斩露头角的导演[[罗伯特·罗德里格兹|罗伯特·罗德里格兹]]和演员安东尼奥·班德拉斯加入了剧组，班德拉斯将出演新一代的佐罗一角<ref>{{cite news | first= Claudia |last= Eller| title = Sony Learns to Schmooze Wall Street| date = 1995-09-22 | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2010-10-23}}</ref>。三星和安伯林公司都对罗德里格兹在《{{link-en|杀手悲歌|El Mariachi}}》和《杀人三步曲》中表现出的低成本电影拍摄技巧倍感惊讶，并且最终取消了与塞洛蒙计划拍摄一部大成本制作佐罗电影的方案<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff| title = 'Desperado' Team Reunited | date = 1995-12-17 | work = Los Angeles Daily News | accessdate = 2010-10-23}}</ref>。斯皮尔伯格本希望罗德里格兹可以在1996年1月开拍并赶在圣诞节档期上映，但这一时间之后被推迟至7月<ref>{{cite news | first = Peter | last = Bart | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117859525 | title = DreamWorks revving up its filmmaking engine | date = 1995-10-29 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2010-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106181610/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117859525 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first= William |last= Arnold| title = 1996 should be a hot year for film | date = 1996-01-10 | work = Seattle Post-Intelligencer | accessdate = 2010-10-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first= Carmina |last= Danini| title = Rodriguez has eye on S.A., Austin area for two new movies| date = 1995-11-17 | work = San Antonio Express-News | accessdate = 2010-10-23}}</ref>，而上映日期也因此不得不跟着推迟至1997年[[复活节|复活节]]左右<ref name=dispute/>。由于与三星影业在影片的预算方面无法达成共识，罗德里格兹于1996年7月退出了剧组。公司计划将预算控制在3500万美元左右，但罗德里格兹则表示需要4500万美元。虽然之后他将数字降至4200万美元时双方均打算达成妥协，但公司最终还是拒绝了这个数字并坚持4100万是预算的最高上限<ref name=dispute>{{cite news | author = Staff| title = Budget Dispute Hangs Up 'Zorro' | date = 1996-06-13 | work = San Jose Mercury News | accessdate = 2010-10-23}}</ref>。不过班德拉斯留了下来，之后[[马丁·坎贝尔|马丁·坎贝尔]]也在当月晚些时候拒绝了执导《[[新鐵金剛之明日帝國|新鐵金剛之明日帝國]]》的机会而加入担任本片的导演<ref>{{cite news |author=Dawtrey, Adam, and Rex Weiner |url=http://www.variety.com/vstory/VR1117436166.html?categoryid=38&cs=1 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106181639/http://www.variety.com/vstory/VR1117436166.html?categoryid=38&cs=1 |archivedate=2012-11-06 |title=MGM's Completion Bond |date=1996-12-30 |work=Variety |accessdate=2013-05-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。而电影最终的剧本则是由{{link-en|约翰·艾斯可|John Eskow}}、{{link-en|泰德·艾略特|Ted Elliott}}、{{link-en|特里·鲁西奥|Terry Rossio}}和{{link-en|兰道尔·约翰逊|Randall Jahnson}}共同完成的<ref>{{cite news | first= James |last= Wolf | title = The Blockbuster Script Factory | date = 1998-08-23 | work = The New York Times}}</ref>。

===拍摄===
影片的主要拍摄工作于1997年1月27日在墨西哥展开，预算为6千万美元<ref name=Flynn>{{cite news | first = Army | last = Archerd | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117466462 | title = Douglases save coastal land | date = 1996-12-09 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2010-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106182207/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117466462 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=escape/>，其中大部分镜头都是在[[首都|首都]][[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]郊区拍摄的<ref name=custom>{{cite news | first = Bashirah | last = Muttalib | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117436609 | title = Rediscovering Mexico | date = 1998-01-16 | work = Variet | accessdate = 2010-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106182033/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117436609 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。不过进入二月份时曾因导演马丁·坎贝尔生病住院治疗而中断了4天，之后再在墨西哥城以东约三小时路程的[[特拉斯卡拉州|特拉斯卡拉]]恢复拍摄，剧组也在这里搭建了所需要的景致和设施<ref>{{cite news | first = Army | last = Archerd | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117863027 | title = Flu fells 'Zorro' director | date = 1997-02-18 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2010-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106182111/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117863027 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。索尼公司派大卫·福斯特作为制片人参与到影片中，来填补斯皮尔伯格的离任留下的空缺。福斯特之后与一位未列名在主创人员名单中的[[剧作家|剧作家]]大卫·沃德（David Ward）一起更改了片中的一些内容<ref name=inside>{{cite news|first=Dan |last=Cox |url=http://www.variety.com/vstory/VR1117342363.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106182812/http://www.variety.com/vstory/VR1117342363.html |archivedate=2012-11-06 |title=Inside Moves |date=1997-03-20 |work=Variety |accessdate=2013-05-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。电影拍摄过程中所遇到的实际困难导致《佐罗的面具》实际成本比预算又增加了一千万美元<ref name=event/>，这让其总成本达到了7千万美元<ref name=inside/>。时间进入12月后，影片的一些道具又再延误了9天之久，这其中包括佐罗的塑胶制剑<ref name=custom/>。最后终于完成而进入后期制作时，斯皮尔伯格和坎贝尔感觉以老佐罗在自己女儿怀抱中去世这样的情节来作为结局实在太郁闷了<ref>{{cite news | first = Army | last = Archerd | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117863191 | title = 'Zorro' ending to stay | date = 1998-01-08 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2010-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106180834/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117863191 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，所以最终将其改成了亚历山卓和艾琳娜成婚后又有了孩子，从此快乐幸福地生活在一起。这一段镜头是在影片拍摄完成3个月后再补拍加进电影中的<ref>{{cite news | first = Army | last = Archerd | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117478404 | title = Berle tribute gets emotional | date = 1998-07-13 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2010-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106182834/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117478404 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

